@startuml MouseManagementSequence
title Mouse speed hotkey flow

actor User as user
participant "hs.hotkey" as hotkey
participant "modules.mouse_management" as mouse
participant "utils.notification_utils" as notification
participant "hs.alert" as alert

autonumber

user -> hotkey: press ctrl+cmd+alt+=
hotkey -> mouse: adjustMouseSpeed(0.1)
mouse -> mouse: log warning (not implemented)
mouse -> notification: announce("mouse_management.mouse_speed_unavailable", payload)
notification -> alert: hs.alert.show(...) (default channel)
alert --> user: informational toast

note right of mouse
`hotkey_utils.bind` disables the built-in overlay while the module routes its
placeholder warning through `notification_utils.announce`.
end note

@enduml
